  <class_name>OCHRE</class_name>
  <display_name>OCHRE Simulator</display_name>
  <description>Runs OCHRE (Object-oriented Controllable High-resolution Residential Energy Model) simulation as an alternative to HPXMLtoOpenStudio/EnergyPlus.</description>
  <modeler_description>This measure replaces the HPXMLtoOpenStudio + EnergyPlus workflow with OCHRE simulation. It takes an HPXML file as input, runs OCHRE via command line, and converts the outputs to match the expected format for downstream reporting measures.</modeler_description>
  <arguments>
